    "Management": {
      "text": "Mild\n: avoid triggers, cool compresses for 15 minutes QID\nModerate\n: Histamine-blocking drops (e.g. naphazoline/pheniramine 0.025%/0.3%, olopatadine, pemirolast, or ketotifen)\nSevere\n: refer to ophthalmology for possible\nsteroid\ntherapy",
